patthana23.29:4.1: Nasekkhaṃ nakusalaṃ dhammaṃ paccayā sekkho kusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana23.29:5.1: Nasekkhaṃ naakusalaṃ dhammaṃ paccayā nevasekkhanāsekkho akusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana23.29:6.1: Nasekkhaṃ naabyākataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nevasekkhanāsekkho abyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana23.29:6.3: Hetuyā pañca, adhipatiyā pañca … pe … avigate pañca.
